
[1]definition

   DEFINITION, n.

   1. A brief description of a thing by its properties; as a definition of
   wit or of a circle.

   2. In logic, the explication of the essence of a thing by its kind and
   difference.

   3. In lexicography, an explanation of the signification of a word or
   term, or of what a word is understood to express.
